author: Xyla Foxlin
description: Another amazing @autodeskuniversity with @Autodesk in the books! It was so fun to be at #AU2025 and meet so many other incredible #Fusion users and creators, learn some new tricks, and hear what's coming down the pipeline! I definitely feel like my CAD game has leveled up, which is always the goal.
title: Autodesk University 2025! #AU2025
